 with .\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">-Each enemy has its own profile</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">-Frenetic Explosion and  Gore: Blood and Guts and special Weapon to slaughter.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"First Blood","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2619280/0a830f18a8af78013e141eace1771ec9c4c76c27.jpg"},{"name":"Level 1","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2619280/b4b9550d09963bae95b114357c62273515bc68b8.jpg"},{"name":"Level 2","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2619280/25a5cb38a949c1dc0386dda4d19ae683933d3ead.jpg"},{"name":"Final Boss Level 3","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2619280/d8f13bd7abb15db7a47e1d378a45dcb122146e29.jpg"},{"name":"Winning Streak of 20 kill","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2619280/d9f385def6005d82867836681c14ee22aceedf84.jpg"},{"name":"Winning Streak of 50 kill","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2619280/dab86e0bf3d684d6c5131706f2670178d7fdf4fe.jpg"},{"name":"Final Boss Level 5","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2619280/3541277d2f074e62ee1308b5dd048a995092cbdc.jpg"},{"name":"Winning Streak of 100 kill","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2619280/370d8b73fcf9252eb10d1df61c8143b2cca2e294.jpg"},{"name":"Final Boss Level 8","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2619280/f2cf0bb2e0a8421cee2abf4026eab69fefa1efda.jpg"}],"total":9},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619280/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1734023724","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2619280/page.bg.jpg?t=1734023724","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstati